cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.GT, cs.NI, cs.CY 

This paper discusses the challenges of preventing cyberattacks through information sharing among organizations, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The proposed model uses functional dependency network analysis and game theory, which are commonly used in social network analysis (cs.SI) and game theory (cs.GT). The simulation framework also involves network settings (cs.NI) and cyberattacks (cs.CY).
